# ChitChat â€“ Emotional AI Chat Companion

**ChitChat** is a mobile app designed for users who feel lonely, need emotional support, or want to explore creative ideas through natural conversations with an AI companion. This case study showcases the complete UX design process from concept to high-fidelity prototype.

